{"tid":1555342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實921元朗靜坐可唔可以改做全港人鏈活動？","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T13:35:15.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7e70db24e1b307e6659b2c34e230a5842d058d","tid":1555342,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZguU0mO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZguU0mO.jpg&h=5360cad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先821我有去元朗靜坐，但現場得一千人左右，noise唔夠大<br />\n<br />\n另外到時狗鐡係可以封元朗站令靜坐搞唔成<br />\n同埋靜坐又可能俾狗話非法集會，又籍機打人捉人<br />\n<br />\n搞一個全港人鏈活動，noise夠大，全和理非，亦較安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家討論一下"},{"pid":"1defbfa9aeb7775e59f02dd1ddde919720ef1353","tid":1555342,"uid":38204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"搞人鏈不如諗個新活動好過<br />\n第二次人鏈個noice一定無咁大"},{"pid":"e6348411ec5b81f3026c8125b29b1336dd3eb1ce","tid":1555342,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:23:52.000Z","msg":"反而係諗住幾區罷工集會"},{"pid":"d3b46d264567daa1ffb1487b6cb1d14e6bb6ccd3","tid":1555342,"uid":94494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"一帶一路峰會將在9月11-12日 在香港會展中心舉行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1495234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1495234</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0113201c2e58d7a136a8534769c4024f4a2a47d6","tid":1555342,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1defbfa9aeb7775e59f02dd1ddde919720ef1353","tid":1555342,"uid":38204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"搞人鏈不如諗個新活動好過<br />\n第二次人鏈個noice一定無咁大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"上次個人鏈只係市區（加少量新界自發）<br />\n<br />\n今次可以全港九新界都做，連接曬全部區"},{"pid":"5dc21521c08f3552fced6d33b6724050a746301e","tid":1555342,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6348411ec5b81f3026c8125b29b1